transcript:
Customer: Hello

Executive: Hello

Customer: Ji sir.

Executive: Sir aap aapne complaint dali hui thi kya issues aa rahe hain aapko?

Customer: Complaint dali hui thi ye IndiaMART ki by lead nahi aa rahi sir.

Executive: Abhi sir hamari last time baat hui thi tab to koi aise issues nahi the na?

Customer: Wo lead hi nahi aa rahi thi us time se bhi maine aapko bol raha tha.

Executive: Achha. Theek hai ek minute aap line pe rahiye check karta hu. Bola tha na maine aapko last time hamari baat hui thi Google meet pe online main bol raha tha aapko us din bhi mere paas mein ek ek lead bhi nahi hai.

Executive: Ek minute main check kar leta hu aap line pe rahiyega sir.

(silence)

Customer: Wo bas maine yahan chali.

Executive: Sir 27 October ko hamari baat hui thi lekin aapne lead ke bare mein mujhe nahi bataya tha koi nahi abhi hum check kar lete hain. Lead ji batai to thi sir maine aapko.

Executive: Chaliye theek hai check kar leta hu. Okay.

Customer: Main aapko bol raha tha ki sir abhi is time lead. But haan haan sorry sorry yaad aa gaya haan bataya tha aapne ki kam aa rahi hai. Aap busy the us time mein.

Customer: Sir ek bhi lead nahi aa rahi hai. Hai na?

Customer: Nahi. Ek bhi lead nahi hai ji mere paas.

Executive: Aapne mobile pe check kiya?

Customer: Mobile pe hi karta hu.

Executive: Ek baar sir abhi recent mein check kijiye.

Customer: Abhi kar raha hu main. Line pe rahiye.

Customer: Tabhi to main aapse keh raha hu ek baar. Sir aapko call kar diya kare mujhe direct mera number aap save kar lijiye aur aapko jo bhi issue hai aap seedha mujhe call kar liya kare.

Customer: Sir mujhe puchna tha ye wala number kiska hoga?

Customer: Kaunsa?

Executive: Batao ek minute sir ye 6377267713.

Customer: Ye bada hi number hai.

Customer: Lead nahi aa rahi sir by lead nahi aa rahi. Kya likha aa raha hai sir?

Customer: Kuch khul hi nahi raha hai home pe ja kar ke to thoda sa khulta hai. Theek hai by lead pe ja kar ke option hoga by lead haan. By lead pe ja kar ke no n o t i f y mail not not female aa raha hai ye kya aa raha hai.

Executive: Theek hai main check kar leta hu.

Customer: Tu bhi to mat ja hai na keva. Bolne matlab Diwali pe to aaja. Diwali.

Customer: Ji sir.

Executive: Sir usme aap upar search kijiye. Kya? Search bar aa raha hoga ek search kijiye marble human statue ya Jaipur murti painter.

Customer: Isme aa nahi raha hai mere paas mein. Human statue and script ye sir lead aa rahi hai Maharana Pratap statue aur mega statue. Ye Nepal se bhi aa rahi hai lead. Silicon black statue realistic man silicon statue. Wo dekho aapke usme system mein aa rahi hai sir mere mein nahi aa rahi.

Executive: Chaliye main aapko guide kar deta hu wahi aap main aapko link send kar deta hu theek hai sir usko aap consume kijiye sorry join kijiye fir main aapko lead consume karwata hu. Theek hai sir. Line pe rahiyega call disconnect mat kijiye ga sir abhi. Theek hai sir lead generate wo link generate karta hu. Theek hai.

Executive: Haan ji.

Executive: Sir phone se hi connect karenge na aap?

Customer: Haan ji haan ji.

Executive: Theek hai. Phone se hi connect hoga.

Customer: Bhejo sir.

Executive: Check kijiye sir aapko maine link send kar diya hai.

Customer: Ye phone kaatne ke baad hi aayega link to. Chaliye theek hai main aap check kijiye ga shorya ke naam se aaya hoga usko aap join kar lijiyega sir. Theek hai.
summary:
Concerns:

- Not receiving buyleads on IndiaMART.

- Wants to call executive directly for issues.



Resolution:

- Executive checked the customer's account.

- Executive will send a link to consume leads.



Next Steps: 

- Customer to join the link sent by executive.



Alert (If Any):

None

- Angry -> Satisfied
